2026-06-25 - Implemented preprocessing pipeline support:
- Added AI/preprocessing/preprocess.py for resizing, letterbox padding, augmentation, mask export, and YOLO segmentation label generation.
- Added AI/preprocessing/__init__.py so the folder can be imported as a reusable package.
- Fixed manifest path resolution so stored paths like mvtec-ad\raw\... resolve correctly under AI/dataset/mvtec-ad.

2026-06-25 - Implemented training pipeline support:
- Added AI/train/train.py with a YOLO segmentation training CLI, automatic data.yaml generation, small-VRAM defaults, and smoke-test mode.
- Added AI/train/__init__.py to make the training folder importable as a package.

2026-06-25 - Fixed training and dataset pipeline issues:
- Updated AI/train/train.py to use Ultralytics-compatible gradient accumulation via nbs instead of invalid accumulate arg.
- Added early label coverage validation in AI/train/train.py to stop training when train/val segmentation labels are empty.
- Fixed AI/dataset/download_mvtec.py to follow MVTec structure (train/test image folders + ground_truth masks) and avoid treating ground_truth mask files as input images.

2026-06-25 - Fixed preprocess manifest compatibility:
- Updated AI/preprocess/preprocess.py path resolution to support workspace-prefixed manifest paths such as AI\dataset\mvtec-ad\raw\... and still resolve correctly under dataset root.

2026-06-25 - Added quality improvement plan:
- Created docs/plan/AIPlan/07_quality_improvement.md to capture the concrete improvement path for low YOLO-seg quality.
- Focus areas: preserve more image detail, validate mask alignment, tune augmentation, compare 10/50/100 epoch runs, and evaluate recall/mAP before retraining.

2026-06-25 - Applied quality-improvement code updates:
- Updated AI/preprocess/preprocess.py to preserve original image resolution, skip defect samples with missing or empty masks, and soften offline augmentation.
- Updated AI/train/train.py to stop forcing preprocess image_size onto training, use a higher default imgsz, audit dataset quality before training, and reduce aggressive online augmentation.
- Training now writes dataset_quality_report.json under AI/train for repeatable comparison of split/class coverage and mask integrity.
